    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织预计经济增长将加速，但仍警告“二十年代不温不火”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/imf-sees-growth-edging-higher-still-warns-of-tepid-twenties</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织暗示，它将小幅上调全球增长预测，同时警告称，如果通胀和债务挑战得不到解决，世界经济在本十年仍面临“不温不火的二十年代”的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-11/imf-sees-growth-edging-higher-still-warns-of-tepid-twenties</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Apr 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
